								>El Poder del Ser</a
							>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="hero-cards">
						<div class="hero-card big">
							<span class="num">50K+</span>
							<span class="lbl">Apoyo Popular</span>
						</div>
						<div class="hero-card">
							<span class="num">100%</span>
							<span class="lbl">Independiente</span>
						</div>
